{"tid":1090786,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：當年49場不敗被球證終結","createTime":"2019-04-03T17:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T01:26:29.000Z","uid":11081,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"371f3c87f8d04796ec5fde9d03322595b7476cbe","tid":1090786,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"格（A.Wenger）已經離開了阿仙奴帥位，但他在阿仙奴歷史上的影響力仍然十分深遠。近日，在接受採訪時雲格回答了有關阿仙奴不敗賽季奪冠的內情。<br />\n<br />\n  在談到2003-04賽季49場不敗奪冠的經歷時，雲格稱：「我們的不敗紀錄被曼聯終結了，但那場比賽球證要承擔一些責任。我們不應該輸波的。順便說一下，如果哪天我死了，上帝讓我選擇去地獄還是去天堂時，我會先問問球證在哪。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我記得之前那個賽季我們作客不敗，但主場失利錯失冠軍。當時所有球員都說我們可以在不敗的情況下奪冠。而在之後奪冠的那個賽季，我對他們說&lsquo;你們是否想要不敗下去？這取決於你們自己&rsquo;。最後我們做到了，我們拿到英超時沒有敗績。」<br />\n<br />\n爺爺好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29285c730c72470207880a4c7db74c1129ffd6d2","tid":1090786,"uid":209773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:09:36.000Z","msg":"49000"},{"pid":"ace84344015b4385b46ac013bed0b68b729629ab","tid":1090786,"uid":45505,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"猁狗又怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5a3688687074f2cbf2bb3d199c5c3e6908765c","tid":1090786,"uid":11081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29285c730c72470207880a4c7db74c1129ffd6d2","tid":1090786,"uid":209773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:09:36.000Z","msg":"49000"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"雲加&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;廢蛇"},{"pid":"14d171cb5edbc59bf2358a1adfc384feb97ce4b3","tid":1090786,"uid":217509,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:14:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57c4974bada5a05e4cdd14b4b0b7b7157b4cfae2","tid":1090786,"uid":11081,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"14d171cb5edbc59bf2358a1adfc384feb97ce4b3","tid":1090786,"uid"